{"tid":1400907,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警方現正沿彌敦道進行驅散行動","createTime":"2019-08-03T13:58:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T14:05:50.000Z","uid":212626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"bb244ae92bd638dbf66353cffd2779745bfe2cde","tid":1400907,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T13:58:35.000Z","msg":"警方現正沿彌敦道進行驅散行動<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n電台及電視台當值宣布員注意：<br />\n<br />\n請盡快播出下列消息，並在適當時間重播：<br />\n<br />\n  由於尖沙咀彌敦道一帶情況急劇惡化，多處地方有縱火及刑事毁壞，主要道路被阻塞，警方現正沿彌敦道進行驅散行動。<br />\n<br />\n  警方呼籲在場人士立即離開，切勿衝擊警方防線。市民如非必要，切勿前往有關地區。<br />\n<br />\n  警方亦呼籲附近一帶居民留意情況，如有需要，應關好窗戶。如非必要，切勿前往相關地區，應留在室內安全地方。<br />\n   <br />\n <br />\n完<br />\n2019年8月3日（星期六）<br />\n香港時間21時41分<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201908/03/P2019080300836.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F201908%2F03%2FP2019080300836.htm&d=PwwdVKvQMhnOdjdmHJS5OYMLxsd%2B2XAbZoZSjzCx9%2B0%3D&h=47a038e8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201908/03/P2019080300836.htm</a>"},{"pid":"2caa23dc0eae0c60c8a78ad835f7438b3c764e8f","tid":1400907,"uid":115977,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T14:05:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>撤呀！全部人撤呀！我要8月5號見到你地！</strong></span></span>"}]}